metadata.name: The Wheat crisis
metadata.description:
Wheat is one of the most important food supply in the world. 
Due to the invasion of Ukraine the price of this primary supply (but also butter, sunflower seed oil, etc) its price skyrocket.
This picture wants to celebrate the importance of this precious good that every summer paints the Italian countryside of gold.

Taken in Canino (Lazio, Italy)

5428x3055
